I want to make more dumplings.

7
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,360
I'm not eating them.

8
00:01:55,670 --> 00:01:56,920
They are all yours.

9
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:02,190
Today is the second day
of the Chinese New Year.

10
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,080
Prepare more dumplings.

11
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:12,080
She's alone in Mi Mansion.

12
00:02:12,670 --> 00:02:15,080
You should go back
and visit her on a day like today.

13
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:47,780
Why are you back?

14
00:02:48,590 --> 00:02:50,190
Today is the second day
of the Chinese New Year.

15
00:02:51,070 --> 00:02:52,950
Mr. Shen and I
made some dumplings for you.

16
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,800
We were worried
that you had nothing to eat.

17
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:57,510
You can have this.

18
00:03:49,230 --> 00:03:49,910
It tastes great.

19
00:03:50,790 --> 00:03:51,880
Delicious.

20
00:03:52,670 --> 00:03:53,560
I never thought

21
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:56,390
that I could eat the dumplings
you made for me.

22
00:04:02,780 --> 00:04:06,670
How did I end up like this?

23
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,160
Do you remember

24
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:16,880
when my birthday is?

25
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:21,100
The 20th day of the 11th month.

26
00:04:22,510 --> 00:04:23,760
On the day I gave birth to you,

27
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:27,630
I almost died due to obstructed labor.

28
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:32,880
Your father didn't even look at us

29
00:04:33,270 --> 00:04:35,030
and took his fifth wife in.

30
00:04:39,830 --> 00:04:42,880
Last year, on the 20th day
of the 11th month,

31
00:04:43,270 --> 00:04:45,670
he held a one-month-old birthday feast
for his eighth wife's son.

32
00:04:46,030 --> 00:04:47,920
I will never forget this day.

33
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:51,470
This is the most humiliating day
in my life.

34
00:04:53,510 --> 00:04:55,120
The 20th day of the 11th month

35
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,880
is also the day I was reborn.

36
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:04,590
I met Mr. Shen on this day.

37
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:06,590
He lets me know

38
00:05:08,030 --> 00:05:09,830
that someone in this world

39
00:05:10,630 --> 00:05:13,240
holds me so dearly.

40
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:17,000
He teaches me how to read, write,

41
00:05:17,510 --> 00:05:19,070
and behave in life.

42
00:05:20,710 --> 00:05:22,240
He teaches me how to love myself

43
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:23,880
and others.

44
00:05:26,442 --> 00:05:28,882
You are supposed to teach me those.

45
00:05:34,150 --> 00:05:35,000
I'm sorry.

46
00:05:36,510 --> 00:05:37,510
Sorry.

47
00:05:37,950 --> 00:05:39,030
So sorry.

48
00:05:39,590 --> 00:05:42,070
I heard your conversation
with Mr. Shen yesterday.

49
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:47,440
He hoped that I could learn
to forgive and let go.

50
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:50,200
I don't wish to disappoint him.

51
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,470
But I really don't know

52
00:05:52,470 --> 00:05:53,950
if you deserve my forgiveness.

53
00:05:55,630 --> 00:05:57,630
Also, I don't know
how to let go of my resentment.

54
00:06:30,630 --> 00:06:32,030
This is my doll.

55
00:06:35,830 --> 00:06:37,440
I saw it in your room. It's wretched,

56
00:06:38,030 --> 00:06:39,470
so I mended it.

57
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:40,800
I didn't think

58
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:43,560
you still have it with you
all these years.

59
00:06:44,630 --> 00:06:46,680
This is the only thing you left me.

60
00:06:55,070 --> 00:06:56,390
After giving birth to you,

61
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,830
I fell sick.

62
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,070
I was afraid that I might infect you,

63
00:07:01,150 --> 00:07:02,440
so I stopped feeding you.

64
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:04,830
I could only put you
in the attic next door.

65
00:07:06,270 --> 00:07:07,710
But they told me

66
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,270
you wouldn't stop crying.

67
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:12,390
I was so worried.

68
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:14,800
I didn't know what to do.

69
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:16,240
So I struggled

70
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:17,830
to make this doll

71
00:07:17,830 --> 00:07:18,800
from my clothes

72
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:19,830
to keep you company.

73
00:07:21,710 --> 00:07:22,920
After having this doll,

74
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,240
you became calmer.

75
00:07:27,270 --> 00:07:29,030
I like this doll very much.

76
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,390
Because you didn't like me

77
00:07:34,510 --> 00:07:35,510
and refused to hold me.

78
00:07:38,590 --> 00:07:40,240
Only this doll stays with me.

79
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,270
To me,

80
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:49,030
this doll has the scent of my mother.

81
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:55,000
Afterward,

82
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,760
I realized that you lost your sight.

83
00:08:02,510 --> 00:08:04,630
Who is to blame?

84
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:08,710
Your father kept on marrying new women.

85
00:08:09,880 --> 00:08:11,470
I couldn't help but become resentful.

86
00:08:12,270 --> 00:08:13,680
I couldn't help but beat you.

87
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:20,760
I... I couldn't control myself.

88
00:08:20,830 --> 00:08:21,700
I just couldn't.

89
00:08:21,700 --> 00:08:23,240
Every time when you beat me,

90
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,760
I would hold it.

91
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,000
That way, my resentment

92
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,270
would lessen.

93
00:08:32,990 --> 00:08:34,640
I even used it to comfort myself

94
00:08:35,100 --> 00:08:36,350
that you didn't mean to beat me.

95
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:38,870
You did it

96
00:08:39,340 --> 00:08:40,470
because you were heartbroken.

97
00:08:41,470 --> 00:08:43,160
I know you didn't have a happy life.

98
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:47,070
And I couldn't help you to keep Father.

99
00:08:49,590 --> 00:08:50,400
No,

100
00:08:52,870 --> 00:08:54,320
it's my fault.

101
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:56,920
Everything was my fault.

102
00:08:59,040 --> 00:08:59,870
Mi Lan,

103
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:02,830
I shouldn't have been trapped
in my own world

104
00:09:03,590 --> 00:09:05,590
and pushed all the blame on you

105
00:09:05,680 --> 00:09:09,040
to put you through all this.
It's all my fault.

106
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:14,470
Forgive me.

107
00:09:24,750 --> 00:09:25,870
I forgive you.

108
00:09:29,230 --> 00:09:30,680
I forgive you.

109
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,320
Mother.

110
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:46,400
Mi Lan.

111
00:09:48,110 --> 00:09:49,110
Mi Lan.

112
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:01,400
Go upstairs.

113
00:10:01,800 --> 00:10:02,590
Now.

114
00:10:02,950 --> 00:10:04,200
Don't come down.

115
00:10:04,470 --> 00:10:04,990
Go upstairs.

116
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:05,800
All right.

117
00:10:06,470 --> 00:10:07,440
Miss Mi Lan,

118
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,800
it has been a long while.

119
00:10:13,040 --> 00:10:14,200
Mu Lihua,

120
00:10:15,160 --> 00:10:16,200
you haven't died yet.

121
00:11:06,710 --> 00:11:07,320
Hello?

122
00:11:07,680 --> 00:11:08,320
(Mr. Shen,)

123
00:11:08,830 --> 00:11:11,040
(Mi Lan was taken away
by a horrible woman.)

124
00:11:11,280 --> 00:11:12,470
What does she look like?

125
00:11:12,710 --> 00:11:14,590
She has a mask on half of her face.

126
00:11:14,680 --> 00:11:17,110
(When she turns her rings,
Mi Lan can't move.)

127
00:11:18,470 --> 00:11:19,750
Only you two were sent?

128
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:23,200
The clan leader said it was your order,
he didn't dare to slight.

129
00:11:23,750 --> 00:11:25,520
Ten Shadow Warriors
have been dispatched,

130
00:11:25,990 --> 00:11:27,200
together two of us,

131
00:11:27,710 --> 00:11:28,800
it should be enough for you.

132
00:11:29,950 --> 00:11:31,990
You unhelpful bunch.

133
00:11:32,590 --> 00:11:34,560
I never expected them to help much.

134
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:36,800
Come with me.

135
00:11:54,185 --> 00:11:55,400
Stop struggling.

136
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:57,230
I have drugged you.

137
00:11:58,110 --> 00:11:59,950
Even Shen Zhiheng couldn't resist it,

138
00:12:00,640 --> 00:12:01,990
let alone you.

139
00:12:06,320 --> 00:12:08,230
What method did Shen Zhiheng use

140
00:12:08,470 --> 00:12:10,040
to restore your sight

141
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:12,440
and give you such power?

142
00:12:12,800 --> 00:12:14,320
Do you expect me to tell you that?

143
00:12:15,990 --> 00:12:17,280
Do you think I won't know

144
00:12:18,110 --> 00:12:19,320
if you don't tell me?

145
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:20,920
Mi Lan,

146
00:12:21,990 --> 00:12:24,750
you are a young girl, and I don't wish
to make it difficult for you.

147
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:28,590
If you can tell me
where the Blood Amber Stone is,

148
00:12:28,950 --> 00:12:30,560
I will release you

149
00:12:30,850 --> 00:12:31,990
so you can reunite with him.

150
00:12:32,590 --> 00:12:33,400
What do you say?

151
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:41,950
I have ways and means to deal with you.

152
00:12:42,590 --> 00:12:44,070
Except for telling me the truth,

153
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,320
you have no other choices.

154
00:12:49,950 --> 00:12:50,920
Mi Lan,

155
00:12:51,520 --> 00:12:53,560
everything is arranged by fate.

156
00:12:53,800 --> 00:12:54,920
It's only a matter of time

157
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:56,560
to find out your secret.

158
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:58,680
Bring Li Yingliang here.

159
00:12:58,800 --> 00:12:59,590
Yes.

160
00:13:33,680 --> 00:13:34,920
You know Li Yingliang, right?

161
00:13:36,350 --> 00:13:38,070
His mind has been manipulated

162
00:13:38,070 --> 00:13:39,400
by my Fantasy Stone.

163
00:13:41,280 --> 00:13:42,640
You may catch up with him

164
00:13:43,160 --> 00:13:44,560
once he wakes up.

165
00:14:36,780 --> 00:14:41,900
(Wei Qiu)

166
00:14:44,950 --> 00:14:45,950
Wei Qiu.

167
00:14:52,520 --> 00:14:54,200
Mu Lihua took Mi Lan away.

168
00:14:54,680 --> 00:14:55,280
What?

169
00:14:55,400 --> 00:14:56,440
Mu Lihua hasn't died yet?

170
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:58,190
Doesn't that mean Mi Lan is in danger?

171
00:14:58,350 --> 00:14:59,830
I found this at Mu Lihua's place.

172
00:15:00,070 --> 00:15:01,950
But I'm not sure
if she left this on purpose.

173
00:15:02,310 --> 00:15:04,650
It's about the secrets
of the Mu family's past generations.

174
00:15:06,710 --> 00:15:09,230
The Mu family is gifted
and possesses the divine ring

175
00:15:09,370 --> 00:15:10,800
that can lure people into illusory.

176
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,920
To ensure the lineage flourishes,

177
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:15,470
the ancestor stole a hibiscus tree
from Mr. Mo

178
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:16,810
and worshipped it for generations.

179
00:15:17,230 --> 00:15:19,470
They sincerely prayed for longevity

180
00:15:19,950 --> 00:15:21,070
but failed to get rid

181
00:15:21,070 --> 00:15:23,280
of the death curse at the age of 30.

182
00:15:26,680 --> 00:15:27,520
Wei Qiu?

183
00:15:32,560 --> 00:15:33,870
They move like ghosts

184
00:15:34,230 --> 00:15:35,870
and can kill in a flash.

185
00:15:36,470 --> 00:15:38,470
The Mu family crafted Shadow Warriors

186
00:15:38,680 --> 00:15:40,160
to injure Wei Qiu in the Year of Shen.

187
00:15:41,470 --> 00:15:42,350
Wei Qiu

188
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:43,830
escaped.

189
00:15:48,590 --> 00:15:50,350
It seems your mother
has kept many secrets

190
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:51,310
that you are unaware of.

191
00:16:21,560 --> 00:16:22,750
Blood Amber Stone.

192
00:17:47,950 --> 00:17:49,510
Where's the Mu family's ship?

193
00:17:50,030 --> 00:17:50,920
According to the plan,

194
00:17:50,930 --> 00:17:52,330
they should reach Haidong very soon.

195
00:17:53,840 --> 00:17:56,400
The Mu family's ship travels in secret
this time,

196
00:17:56,440 --> 00:17:57,470
they can't dock.

197
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:01,400
Take Mi Lan to the ship first.

198
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:03,360
Meet with our ship at sea.

199
00:18:06,030 --> 00:18:06,950
With her,

200
00:18:08,600 --> 00:18:11,200
Shen Zhiheng
will hand himself over to us.

201
00:18:16,120 --> 00:18:18,080
I have some past grudges

202
00:18:19,230 --> 00:18:21,920
that need to be settled
with Shen Zhiheng.

203
00:18:46,310 --> 00:18:47,470
Why are there so many crows?

204
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:48,600
Urgh.

205
00:18:54,920 --> 00:18:57,200
Haidong Army is insane!

206
00:18:57,200 --> 00:18:58,140
Run!

207
00:18:58,140 --> 00:18:59,140
Run now!

208
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:00,760
Hurry!

209
00:19:00,800 --> 00:19:01,640
Run!

210
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:03,180
Liang.

211
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:24,080
Jingxue, this is the key to my home.

212
00:19:24,260 --> 00:19:25,920
Stay inside and do not come out.

213
00:19:26,230 --> 00:19:27,560
If I see Li Yingliang,

214
00:19:27,560 --> 00:19:28,860
I will definitely bring him back.

215
00:19:29,740 --> 00:19:30,540
Weilian.

216
00:19:33,380 --> 00:19:34,480
It's also important

217
00:19:35,350 --> 00:19:36,550
that you can come back safely.

218
00:20:09,160 --> 00:20:09,750
Zhiheng,

219
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:10,790
did Mu Lihua

220
00:20:10,790 --> 00:20:11,920
gather all three meteorites?

221
00:20:12,270 --> 00:20:13,030
If she does,

222
00:20:13,480 --> 00:20:15,270
will you still come with me
for the rescue?

223
00:20:16,200 --> 00:20:17,180
I see you as my brother.

224
00:20:17,270 --> 00:20:18,470
I go where you go.

225
00:20:19,230 --> 00:20:21,080
Even though we might die?

226
00:20:21,920 --> 00:20:23,200
I am not

227
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:24,920
a coward.

228
00:20:25,990 --> 00:20:27,030
I may have been before,

229
00:20:27,360 --> 00:20:29,400
but now I have someone
I want to protect.

230
00:20:32,160 --> 00:20:34,080
As of now, no one can fight
against Mu Lihua.

231
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:35,800
Her power is beyond a human being.

232
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:38,120
The karma caused by the three meteorites

233
00:20:38,710 --> 00:20:40,310
should end on us.

234
00:20:41,030 --> 00:20:42,710
Locate Mu Lihua first.

235
00:20:43,310 --> 00:20:43,880
All right.

236
00:20:45,300 --> 00:20:46,120
- Mr. Mo.
- Mr. Mo.

237
00:20:46,200 --> 00:20:47,120
Finally, I found you.

238
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:48,230
Mu Lihua has likely

239
00:20:48,230 --> 00:20:49,600
gathered all three meteorites.

240
00:20:49,710 --> 00:20:51,510
No, she only got two.

241
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:52,440
I have found her.

242
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:54,050
She's in the volcano cave
outside of the city.

243
00:20:54,080 --> 00:20:56,190
She manipulates many Haidong soldiers
with the Fantasy Stone

244
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:57,180
and is hurting everyone.

245
00:20:57,480 --> 00:20:58,840
Two of you, come with me.

246
00:20:59,120 --> 00:21:01,230
I believe if we join hands,
we can stop her.

247
00:21:01,550 --> 00:21:03,440
But the traffic outside the city
is paralyzed.

248
00:21:03,710 --> 00:21:04,840
How do we get there?

249
00:21:04,950 --> 00:21:05,710
I have an idea.

250
