(Emergency news!)

251
00:21:08,480 --> 00:21:10,820
(Acting Superintendent Wu
has dispatched the Haidong Army)

252
00:21:10,820 --> 00:21:12,750
(to patrol all the streets of Haidong)

253
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:14,510
(to ensure the safety of the citizens.)

254
00:21:14,750 --> 00:21:16,680
(Citizens, please do not panic.)

255
00:21:16,680 --> 00:21:19,440
(Stay at home and take precautions.
Lock the doors and windows.)

256
00:21:19,440 --> 00:21:21,030
(Do not go out
without necessary reasons)

