00:21:21,030 --> 00:21:23,640
(Emergency news!)

258
00:21:26,030 --> 00:21:26,840
Move back, everyone.

259
00:21:27,440 --> 00:21:28,550
Run this way! Quick.

260
00:21:29,180 --> 00:21:30,080
Over there.

261
00:21:31,820 --> 00:21:32,710
Save the injured first.

262
00:21:32,780 --> 00:21:33,680
Save the injured first.

263
00:21:59,080 --> 00:21:59,880
Run!

264
00:22:16,980 --> 00:22:17,950
I will go and stop them.

265
00:22:18,160 --> 00:22:19,270
Two of you, go and save her.

266
00:22:19,360 --> 00:22:20,030
Be careful.

267
00:22:20,030 --> 00:22:20,470
All right.

268
00:22:23,240 --> 00:22:24,200
Hyah!

269
00:22:26,600 --> 00:22:27,200
Hyah!

270
00:22:30,060 --> 00:22:30,680
Hyah!

271
00:22:46,740 --> 00:22:47,420
What...

272
00:22:47,710 --> 00:22:49,310
What is this sound?

273
00:22:49,920 --> 00:22:51,190
I encountered it when I was little.

274
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:53,640
This is an omen
of the falling Heavenly Fire.

275
00:22:54,120 --> 00:22:54,880
Heavenly Fire?

276
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:55,790
Save us!

277
00:22:55,790 --> 00:22:57,310
Let us out!

278
00:22:57,750 --> 00:22:58,880
Is anyone there?

279
00:22:59,230 --> 00:23:00,950
- Let us out!
- Is anyone there?

280
00:23:02,360 --> 00:23:03,440
Anyone?

